{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS Phase 2 registry/router verification (no markdown fences). #}
{# Version: 2026.04.19.2 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-19 #}

{# =========================
  Phase 2 Registry/Router Verification (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: validate read-only Phase 2 surfaces after rebuild/validate services.
  Note: supports both entity-id styles:
    - sensor.shadow_* (has_entity_name enabled)
    - sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_* (older/manual naming assumptions)
  Workflow:
    1) Run actions: spectra_ls.rebuild_registry + spectra_ls.validate_contracts
    2) Reload this template and inspect verdict + trace details
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}
{% set s_hosts = 'sensor.shadow_control_hosts' if states['sensor.shadow_control_hosts'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_control_hosts' %}
{% set b_capable = 'binary_sensor.shadow_active_control_capable' if states['binary_sensor.shadow_active_control_capable'] is not none else 'binary_sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_capable' %}

{% set active_target = states(s_target) %}
{% set active_path = states(s_path) %}
{% set control_hosts = states(s_hosts) %}
{% set control_capable = is_state(b_capable,'on') %}

{% set target_exists = states[s_target] is not none %}
{% set path_exists = states[s_path] is not none %}
{% set hosts_exists = states[s_hosts] is not none %}
{% set capable_exists = states[b_capable] is not none %}

{% set parity_unresolved = state_attr(s_target,'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set parity_mismatches = state_attr(s_target,'mismatches') or [] %}
{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target,'captured_at') %}
{% set registry = state_attr(s_target,'registry') or {} %}
{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target,'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract_validation = state_attr(s_target,'contract_validation') or {} %}

{% set captured_dt = as_datetime(captured_at) if captured_at not in [none,'','none','unknown','unavailable'] else none %}
{% set snapshot_age_s = ((as_timestamp(now()) - as_timestamp(captured_dt)) | int) if captured_dt is not none else none %}
{% set freshness_ok = snapshot_age_s is not none and snapshot_age_s <= 300 %}

{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set route_reason = route_trace.reason if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.reason is defined else '' %}
{% set route_trace_ok = route_decision not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] %}

{% set contract_ready = contract_validation is mapping and contract_validation.valid is defined %}
{% set contract_valid = contract_validation.valid if contract_ready else false %}
{% set contract_missing_required = contract_validation.missing_required if contract_ready and contract_validation.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set contract_ok = contract_ready and contract_valid and (contract_missing_required | length) == 0 %}

{% set legacy_target = states('sensor.ma_active_target') %}
{% set legacy_path = states('sensor.ma_active_control_path') %}
{% set legacy_hosts = states('sensor.ma_control_hosts') %}
{% set legacy_capable = states('binary_sensor.ma_active_control_capable') %}

{% set route_ok = (active_target not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable']) and (active_path not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable']) %}
{% set parity_ok = (parity_unresolved | length) == 0 and (parity_mismatches | length) == 0 %}
{% set host_hint_ok = control_hosts not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] %}
{% set legacy_ready = legacy_target not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] and legacy_path not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] and legacy_hosts not in ['','none','unknown','unavailable'] %}

{% set shadow_entities_present = target_exists and path_exists and hosts_exists %}

{% set score = 0 %}
{% if route_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if control_capable %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if parity_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if host_hint_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if shadow_entities_present %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if freshness_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if route_trace_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if contract_ok %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}

{% set verdict = 'PASS' %}
{% if score < 5 %}
  {% set verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif score < 8 %}
  {% set verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### Phase 2 Registry/Router Verification (`spectra_ls`)
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**
- Score: **{{ score }}/8**

### Shadow parity surfaces
- Target sensor (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ active_target }}** (exists={{ target_exists }})
- Path sensor (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ active_path }}** (exists={{ path_exists }})
- Capable binary (`{{ b_capable }}`): **{{ control_capable }}** (exists={{ capable_exists }})
- Hosts sensor (`{{ s_hosts }}`): **{{ control_hosts }}** (exists={{ hosts_exists }})
- Captured-at: **{{ captured_at if captured_at is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- Snapshot freshness (<=300s): **{{ freshness_ok }}** (age_s={{ snapshot_age_s if snapshot_age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

### Internal diagnostics surfaces
- Registry target count: **{{ registry.target_count if registry is mapping and registry.target_count is defined else 'n/a' }}**
- Route decision/reason: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}** / **{{ route_reason if route_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Route trace present: **{{ route_trace_ok }}**
- Contract validation ready/valid: **{{ contract_ready }} / {{ contract_valid }}**
- Missing required contract entities: **{{ contract_missing_required | length }}**

### Legacy upstream status (source-of-truth surfaces)
- `sensor.ma_active_target`: **{{ legacy_target }}**
- `sensor.ma_active_control_path`: **{{ legacy_path }}**
- `sensor.ma_control_hosts`: **{{ legacy_hosts }}**
- `binary_sensor.ma_active_control_capable`: **{{ legacy_capable }}**
- Legacy routing ready: **{{ legacy_ready }}**

### Parity status
- Unresolved sources count: **{{ parity_unresolved | length }}**
- Mismatch count: **{{ parity_mismatches | length }}**

{% if (parity_unresolved | length) > 0 %}
Unresolved sources:
{% for item in parity_unresolved %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (parity_mismatches | length) > 0 %}
Parity mismatches:
{% for item in parity_mismatches %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (contract_missing_required | length) > 0 %}
Missing required contract entities:
{% for item in contract_missing_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

### Suggested actions
- Service: `spectra_ls.rebuild_registry`
- Service: `spectra_ls.validate_contracts`
- Service: `spectra_ls.dump_route_trace`

### Guidance
{% if verdict == 'PASS' %}
- Phase 2 read-only registry/router parity looks deterministic.
{% elif not shadow_entities_present %}
- Shadow entities are missing from the registry. Verify the `spectra_ls` config entry is loaded and integration entities are enabled.
{% elif not freshness_ok %}
- Snapshot looks stale (>300s). Run services again and verify `captured_at` advances before trusting PASS.
{% elif not legacy_ready %}
- Legacy source entities are still unknown/unavailable (common during reboot settling). Wait for MA control surfaces to populate, then rerun services.
{% elif not route_ok %}
- Active target/path parity surfaces are unresolved. Verify legacy routing entities and rerun services.
{% elif not route_trace_ok %}
- Route trace diagnostics missing; run `spectra_ls.dump_route_trace` and confirm trace attributes populate.
{% elif not control_capable %}
- Target currently reports not control-capable. Confirm room/host mapping for selected target.
{% elif not contract_ok %}
- Contract validation is incomplete or invalid. Run `spectra_ls.validate_contracts` and resolve missing required entities.
{% elif not parity_ok %}
- Legacy/component parity drift detected. Resolve unresolved sources or mismatches before next slice.
{% else %}
- Partial degradation detected; rerun services and compare captured-at/mismatch deltas.
{% endif %}
